headline: AT&T Contributes $9.3 Million to Human-I-T to Bridge Connectivity Gap
summary: Underscoring a bold and enduring commitment to digital equity, Human-I-T today announced a transformative $9.3 million contribution from AT&T, deepening a partnership dedicated to closing the digital divide for underserved communities nationwide.
